*Zadovoljstvo* je učiniti nešto dobro drugima. (The pleasure is to do something good for others.)
Uživala je u *zadovoljstvu* koje je donelo uspeh. (She enjoyed the pleasure of success.)
Mnogi ljudi pokazuju *zadovoljstvo* kada se sreću sa starim prijateljima. (Many people show pleasure when they meet old friends.)
*Zadovoljstvo* je bilo ponovno videti ga posle duže vremena. (The pleasure was to see him again after a long time.)
Ona je uživala u *zadovoljstvu* da čuje njegove divne melodije. (She enjoyed the pleasure of hearing his wonderful melodies.)